WEBVTT

00:09:56.735 --> 00:10:02.268
Judge Bowen sent him home
with maps and checklists and handouts

00:10:02.292 --> 00:10:05.877
and recommended instead
vocational rehabilitation

00:10:05.901 --> 00:10:08.868
and flexible scheduling
for those therapies.

00:10:09.479 --> 00:10:13.010
And this with those supports,
Mike's back to work

00:10:13.034 --> 00:10:16.541
for the first time since his injury
while he was in the service.

00:10:16.565 --> 00:10:19.568
He's repairing relationships
with his family,

00:10:19.592 --> 00:10:21.602
and just last month,

00:10:21.626 --> 00:10:24.631
he graduated from
Judge Bowen's veteran's court.

00:10:25.322 --> 00:10:28.866
(Applause)